                            <comment id="14454183" author="dfabulich" created="Thu, 7 Feb 2008 20:10:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I reproduce the problem, but I find that the integration test TestNgSuiteXmlTest fails when I apply this patch:&lt;/p&gt;

